use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 04, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104byy1665703005368.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/byy1665703005368.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/byy1665703005368.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"byy1665703005368\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"byy1665703005368__moveocc_228723\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Move the field values of the current occurrence to another occurrence.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"byy1665703005368__topic_d74405e1_d74406e1_d74407e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"byy1665703005368__p_d74408e1_d74409e1_d74410e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">moveocc</span> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span>}\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceNumber</var> {<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldList</var>}</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"byy1665703005368__p_d74411e1_d74412e1_d74413e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">moveocc/allfields</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceNumber</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"byy1665703005368__section_w1730ab1b7b5_w1731ab1b7_w1732ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"byy1665703005368__p_d74414e1_d74415e1_d74416e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">moveocc vEntity, -1, vFields</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"byy1665703005368__topic_d49037e1_d49038e1_d49039e1_d49040e1_d49041e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d971046e103\">\n                       \n Qualifiers\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6944e1_d6945e1_d6946e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Qualifiers</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6944e1_d6945e1_d6946e1__entry__1\">\n Qualifier\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6944e1_d6945e1_d6946e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6944e1_d6945e1_d6946e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/allfields</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6944e1_d6945e1_d6946e1__entry__2\">\n All the fields are copied.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"byy1665703005368__topic_d49042e1_d49043e1_d49044e1_d49045e1_d49046e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d971046e149\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6947e1_d6948e1_d6949e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6947e1_d6948e1_d6949e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6947e1_d6948e1_d6949e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6947e1_d6948e1_d6949e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6947e1_d6948e1_d6949e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6947e1_d6948e1_d6949e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6947e1_d6948e1_d6949e1__entry__3\">\n Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6947e1_d6948e1_d6949e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6947e1_d6948e1_d6949e1__entry__2\">\n Number\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6947e1_d6948e1_d6949e1__entry__3\">\n Number of the occurrence to which the current occurrence of the fields in the <var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldList</var> will be moved. Must be a whole (integer) number; the value will be truncated to form an integer.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6947e1_d6948e1_d6949e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldList</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6947e1_d6948e1_d6949e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6947e1_d6948e1_d6949e1__entry__3\">\n Comma-separated list of fields to be moved to the specified occurrence. If no <var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldList</var> is provided, no fields are copied.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"byy1665703005368__topic_d49047e1_d49048e1_d49049e1_d49050e1_d49051e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d971046e240\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6950e1_d6951e1_d6952e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6950e1_d6951e1_d6952e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6950e1_d6951e1_d6952e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6950e1_d6951e1_d6952e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6950e1_d6951e1_d6952e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span>\n\t\tcontains the exact error.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6950e1_d6951e1_d6952e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&gt;=0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6950e1_d6951e1_d6952e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Statement was successful. The exact number equals the sequence number of the new current occurrence.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 4. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">moveocc</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1203</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_RANGE&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value out of range.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1101</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_FIELD&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n An incorrect field name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically or the field is not available in the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-302</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">-303</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UVALERR_KEY_*&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"byy1665703005368__table_d6953e1_d6954e1_d6955e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Key incorrect.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"byy1665703005368__topic_d49052e1_d49053e1_d49054e1_d49055e1_d49056e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d971046e445\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"byy1665703005368__d6507e20\">Allowed in all component types except Dynamic and Static Server Pages.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"byy1665703005368__topic_d49057e1_d49058e1_d49059e1_d49060e1_d49061e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d971046e454\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"byy1665703005368__p_d74435e1_d74436e1_d74437e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">moveocc</span> statement moves the fields of the current occurrence of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> (whether they have been modified or not) that are specified in the <var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldList</var> to the target <var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceNumber</var>. The target occurrence then becomes the new current occurrence and the old current occurrence is deleted.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"byy1665703005368__p_d74438e1_d74439e1_d74440e1\">The ProcScript function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldmod</span> is set to value 1 (modified) for all fields copied to the target occurrence. Other modification-related functions such as <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occmod</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occdbmod</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancemod,</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancedbmod</span> are set to 1 (modified) accordingly. Validation functions such as <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keyvalidation</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$occvalidation</span>, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$instancevalidation</span> are also set to 1 (requires validation) accordingly.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"byy1665703005368__section_vjp_hgh_ybc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d971046e503\">Example: Moving Field Values to Another Occurrence</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example moves the current values of the fields in the\n            variable $FIELDS$ in entity, ENT, to the occurrence stated in\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">$result</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"byy1665703005368__pre_g3b_3gh_ybc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; find occurrence with same key\n; update occurrence\n\noperation uupdate ENT\nparams\n occurrence pEntity :IN\nendparams\n\nfindkey pEntity \nmoveocc pEntity, $result, $fields$\n\nend ; end occurrence\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rjy1665702601052.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$fieldmod</a><p>Return the modification status of a field.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eai1665702600334.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occmod</a><p>Return the modification status of an occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uli1665702604314.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occdbmod</a><p>Return the modification status of a database occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/atw1665702600492.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancemod</a><p>Return or set the modification status of data in the current component instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/len1665702601301.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancedbmod</a><p>Return the modification status of database fields in the current component instance.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wcw1719485700746.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$keyvalidation</a><p>Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpz1719812992669.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$occvalidation</a><p>Check whether an occurrence requires validation.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/biz1719502191613.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$instancevalidation</a><p>Identify whether data in the component instance requires validation.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526319\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526319\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "moveocc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 04, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Move the field values of the current occurrence to another occurrence. moveocc { Entity , } OccurrenceNumber { , FieldList } moveocc/allfields Entity , OccurrenceNumber Example: moveocc vEntity, -1, vFields Qualifiers Table 1. Qualifiers Qualifier Description /allfields All the fields are copied. Parameters Table 2. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used. OccurrenceNumber Number Number of the occurrence to which the current occurrence of the fields in the FieldList will be moved. Must be a whole (integer) number; the value will be truncated to form an integer. FieldList String Comma-separated list of fields to be moved to the specified occurrence. If no FieldList is provided, no fields are copied. Return Values Table 3. Values returned in $status Value Description <0 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. >=0 Statement was successful. The exact number equals the sequence number of the new current occurrence. Table 4. Values returned by $procerror following moveocc Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. -1203 <UPROCERR_RANGE> Value out of range. -1101 <UPROCERR_FIELD> An incorrect field name was provided; either the field name is not valid syntactically or the field is not available in the component. -302 , -303 <UVALERR_KEY_*> Key incorrect. Use Allowed in all component types except Dynamic and Static Server Pages. Description The moveocc statement moves the fields of the current occurrence of Entity (whether they have been modified or not) that are specified in the FieldList to the target OccurrenceNumber . The target occurrence then becomes the new current occurrence and the old current occurrence is deleted. The ProcScript function $fieldmod is set to value 1 (modified) for all fields copied to the target occurrence. Other modification-related functions such as $occmod , $occdbmod , $instancemod, and $instancedbmod are set to 1 (modified) accordingly. Validation functions such as $keyvalidation , $occvalidation , and $instancevalidation are also set to 1 (requires validation) accordingly. Example: Moving Field Values to Another Occurrence The following example moves the current values of the fields in the variable $FIELDS$ in entity, ENT, to the occurrence stated in $result . ; find occurrence with same key ; update occurrence operation uupdate ENT params occurrence pEntity :IN endparams findkey pEntity moveocc pEntity, $result, $fields$ end ; end occurrence Copy Related Links $fieldmod Return the modification status of a field. $occmod Return the modification status of an occurrence. $occdbmod Return the modification status of a database occurrence. $instancemod Return or set the modification status of data in the current component instance. $instancedbmod Return the modification status of database fields in the current component instance. $keyvalidation Identify whether a primary or candidate key requires validation. $occvalidation Check whether an occurrence requires validation. $instancevalidation Identify whether data in the component instance requires validation. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}